div.div:
Since it is not a double dispatch, there is no accept method on the IConstruct or Bucket side to pass itself (this) to the Visitor.
When synthesizing, the recurse function in the synthesize function (aws-cdk-lib/core/lib/private/synthesis.ts), recursively starting from the Stack (root of the tree) as an ObjectStructure, it obtains a list of IAspects (Visitor) from its own IConstruct via Aspects so that the Visitor can access the IConstruct.
synthesize
---->invokeAspects
-------->recurse
-----------
->Loop with the aspect corresponding to the own Construct taken by Aspects.of
---------------
->aspect.visit
-----------
->
Loop in node.children of own Construct
---------------->recurse (per childConstruct)
